         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the Divine Spirits. Costitutia Concordia lived for fifteen years and
               thirty days. Cositutia Apra and Julius Afobianus, (her) son, made this for a
               well-deserving, most beloved (and) most extraordinary mother. </p>
         </div>
